PrecisAuthorization of the appointment of the HONOURABLE JULIUS ISAAC, a Justice of the Federal Court of Appeal, to serve on the Commission of Inquiry into the upsurge of criminal violence since May 2001 in a number of Jamaican urban communities, for a period of six months, effective September 1, 2001.

precis:
Authorization of the appointment of the HONOURABLE JULIUS ISAAC, a Justice
of the Federal Court of Appeal, to serve on the Commission of Inquiry into
the upsurge of criminal violence since May 2001 in a number of Jamaican
urban communities, for a period of six months, effective September 1,
2001.
